      "description": "This car is in good condition. The exterior has a clean finish with only minor surface imperfections that are typical for its age. The interior shows light wear on the upholstery and trim but remains in solid, functional shape. Mechanically, the car runs well with no known issues.",
      "price": 34000.0,
